'''Dame Josephine Barstow''' [[Order of the British Empire|DBE]] (born [[September 27]], [[1940]], [[Sheffield, England]]) is an [[English people|English]] [[soprano]].
Josephine Barstow was created a [[Order of the British Empire|Dame Commander of the British Empire]] in [[1995]].
